general.description:
Shameera Prajapriya has over a decade of corporate experience within the field of Information Technology. He is a Solutions Architect by Profession, currently leads the WebQuarters Group. Shameera hold several accolades including MVP – Azure, hence a rare talent. 

He is a well experienced professional in architecting cloud based solutions and developing innovative application using various programming languages such as .Net, C# / MVC, PHP and 4GL Languages like Progress. Further his passion is innovating devices (IoT) to provide better solutions for the customer requirements using microprocessor / electronics & etc.;

In addition, he is a Technical Speaker and the Founder of Azure IoT Squad. He is also an Ambassador, micro: bit SLUG. His ability to think out of the box made him one of the chief contributors towards achieving an APICTA Award for his product developed for LAUGFS International - GnTracker, which was awarded a merit award in Thailand, in 2016.
